WEBVTT

00:02.790 --> 00:06.807
More than 100 billion words are translated every day.

00:06.931 --> 00:07.869
Lift your hand.

00:08.017 --> 00:09.608
Thank you very much for your help.

00:12.525 --> 00:13.599
Words about food.

00:18.294 --> 00:26.123
Words about friendship, about sport, about belief, about fear.

00:27.788 --> 00:28.641
Oh my god!

00:28.780 --> 00:32.945
Words that can hurt and sometimes divide.

00:34.540 --> 00:39.183
But every day, the most translated words in the world...

00:40.823 --> 00:47.747
...are "how are you," "thank you" and "I love you."

